  "2209890": {
    "name": "House Hopper",
    "steam_appid": 2209890,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/54e59c6c1083bc05a3e2d4b6c395a5e3.avif?t=1731078711\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/b6a6e4571668611c1a4fe0eb475f28d4.poster.avif?t=1731078711\" width=626 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/b6a6e4571668611c1a4fe0eb475f28d4.webm?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/b6a6e4571668611c1a4fe0eb475f28d4.mp4?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i><strong>跳跃、坠落、撞毁、一次又一次！</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从一个地方跳到另一个地方，收集所有钥匙！把自己发射出去，穿过多个房间，尝试降落在狭小的地方。让物理学为你所用！设法离开房子！但要小心，这项终极跳跃运动并不容易。不断的坠落和和碰撞会将你的决心和冷静推向极限。可别说我们没提前警告你哦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/247253ae75fb1b790be99cf087e87a0f.poster.avif?t=1731078711\" width=626 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/247253ae75fb1b790be99cf087e87a0f.webm?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/247253ae75fb1b790be99cf087e87a0f.mp4?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i><strong>收集钥匙，解锁新关卡！</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过这个名为“房子”的硬核障碍赛道。听起来很简单，是不是？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个房间都是一个全新的挑战，其中有独特的危险、各种各样的谜题，当然还有一条通关之路，但你要历经千辛万苦才能取胜！祝你好运！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/4ddbcaa655660a433398d8909ebb3d17.poster.avif?t=1731078711\" width=626 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/4ddbcaa655660a433398d8909ebb3d17.webm?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/4ddbcaa655660a433398d8909ebb3d17.mp4?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i><strong>避开危险！</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获取所有钥匙、一路跳跃通过各个关卡并寻找新的可玩物品，同时尽量不要死太多次。不要烧焦、触电，或因为重力而摔落在地。失败的方法五花八门，但也有很多获胜的方法！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/08b6a1cf4abae2edebf71df80ea688e0.poster.avif?t=1731078711\" width=626 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/08b6a1cf4abae2edebf71df80ea688e0.webm?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/08b6a1cf4abae2edebf71df80ea688e0.mp4?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i><strong>解锁更多可玩物品！</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿过房子，通过与（不那么）随机的物品互动，解锁所有可玩的物品！每件物品都有独特的物理特性和使用方法。找出对应的特性，并找到新的方法来巧夺高分！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/6160b28c2839fb3deea4b3c934c73981.poster.avif?t=1731078711\" width=626 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/6160b28c2839fb3deea4b3c934c73981.webm?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209890/extras/6160b28c2839fb3deea4b3c934c73981.mp4?t=1731078711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>关于高分！</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到新的捷径，使用新的可玩物品，学习精确控制。刷新自己的最高分，并在积分榜上查看自己的进度！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>立即开玩！</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● \t一路跳跃穿过极具挑战的关卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● \t收集钥匙，解锁房子里的所有房间</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● \t找到所有可玩物品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● \t刷新你的最高分</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● \t解开一个个谜题</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● \t坠落</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● \t更厉害的坠落</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● \t碰撞、砸毁、燃烧</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● \t不断重复</p>",
